    "MethodologyIn this study, we propose a multimodal emotion recognition method based on tensor decomposition fusion and self-supervised multi-task learning.",
    "As illustrated in Figure 1, we first extract features from each unimodal data; subsequently, these features are integrated using a tensor fusion method, and dimensionality reduction is applied to the fused data using Tucker decomposition.",
    "Following this, we conduct multimodal emotion recognition tasks and employ a label generation module for unimodal tasks to perform comprehensive prediction and analysis.Multi-Modal Emotion Recognition Using Tensor Decomposition Fusion and Self-Super UNIMODAL FEATURE EXTRACTIONIn multimodal emotion recognition research, the extraction of features from individual modalities is crucial for the subsequent fusion process.",
